You can transfer your data directly to Garmin Connect (a web-based community of Garmin users who track, explore and share activities) or Garmin Training Center (software to analyze activities and create workouts). Be able to have complete control of the workouts you do using the Garmin USB stick to your advantage. Track your goals and the changes that you've made over time right from your computer.
items.longDescription: <br><b>Garmin USB ANT Stick:</b><ul><li>Plugs into computer's USB port</li><li>Automatically receives activity data when compatible fitness device is within range</li><li>Allows access to Garmin Training Center</li><li>The USB GPS is able to work when you're within range of your computer</li><li>Track and record all of your workout progress</li><li>Keep goals and speak with others within the Garmin workout community</li></ul>

The Samsung Note 5 smartphone is bluetooth capable, so you can use it hands free as needed. It has a convenient, front-facing 5MP camera with optical stabilization, so your pictures are crisp and clean. The Samsung Galaxy Smartphone N920G brings reliable service and in a sleek style.

items.name: Garmin Vehicle Power Cable
items.shortDescription: <p>The sleek Garmin Vehicle Power Cable is designed to quickly and easily power your Oregon, Colorado and GPS Map 62 series. Simply plug it into a 12V cigarette lighter to power your device and conserve its battery life. The GPS power cable comes with a 1.5A replaceable fuse designed to add protection to your device during use. This product is easy to engage and disengage, making it ideal for use in multiple vehicles. Use this convenient cable to keep your GPS unit alive throughout all of your trips. The Garmin cable is long enough to plug into a mounted unit, giving you flexibility in how you use your navigation system.</p>
items.longDescription: <br><b>Garmin Vehicle Power Cable:</b><ul><li>12V cigarette lighter adapter</li><li>Includes a 1.5A replaceable fuse</li><li>The GPS power cable is compatible with Oregon, Colorado and GPS Map 62 series</li><li>Power your device and conserve its battery life</li><li>This Garmin cable is easy to engage and disengage</li></ul>

items.name: Garmin Suction Cup Mount
items.shortDescription: The adjustable Garmin Suction Cup Mount allows you to easily access your compatible device while navigating in your vehicle. For easy viewing, mount your device to your windshield with the suction cup or attach the adhesive disc to your dashboard.
items.longDescription: <br><b>Garmin Suction Cup Mount:</b><ul><li>Adjustable</li><li>Mount to windshield or adhesive disc</li><li>Compatible with Nuvi 200, 200W, 250, 250W, 255, 255W, 260, 260W, 265Wt, 270, 275T and 465T</li></ul>
